Top Hair Color and Balayage Trends
Dubai is a hub of fashion and beauty, and its hair salons are no exception. Here are some of the top hair color and balayage trends you can explore at Code Hair and other top salons in the city:

1. Balayage
Balayage is a popular technique that involves hand-painting highlights onto the hair to create a natural, sun-kissed look. This versatile technique can be customized to suit any hair color and length, making it a favorite among women in Dubai. For the best balayage in Dubai, Code Hair is the top choice.

2. Ombre
Ombre hair color transitions from a darker shade at the roots to a lighter shade at the ends. This trendy look can be subtle or bold, depending on your preference, and is perfect for adding depth and dimension to your hair.

3. Highlights and Lowlights
Highlights and lowlights are classic techniques that add contrast and movement to your hair. Whether you opt for subtle or dramatic highlights, these techniques can enhance your natural hair color and give you a fresh, vibrant look.

4. Bold Colors
For those looking to make a statement, bold hair colors like vibrant reds, blues, and purples are a great option. Code Hair’s expert stylists can help you choose the perfect shade to complement your skin tone and personality. This makes Code Hair a premier destination for hair color for women in Dubai .

5. Natural Shades
Natural shades like caramel, honey, and chocolate brown are always in style. These colors add warmth and richness to your hair, creating a sophisticated and timeless look.

Other Exceptional Hair Treatments in Dubai
While Code Hair is the epitome of excellence in hair color and balayage, Dubai is home to many other salons offering exceptional hair treatments. Here are some must-try treatments available in the city:

1. Keratin Treatments
Keratin treatments are designed to smooth and strengthen your hair, reducing frizz and enhancing shine. This treatment is perfect for those looking to achieve sleek, manageable hair.

2. Hair Extensions
Hair extensions are a great way to add length and volume to your hair. Dubai’s top salons offer a variety of extension types, including clip-ins, tape-ins, and micro-link extensions, to suit your needs.

3. Scalp Treatments
Scalp treatments can improve the health of your scalp and hair. These treatments often include deep cleansing, exfoliation, and moisturizing to promote hair growth and overall scalp health.

